data.description: This charming 850 sq ft bungalow! Boasting 3 bedrooms and beautifully refinished hardwood floors, this home exudes warmth and comfort. Abundant natural light fills every corner, creating an inviting ambiance.Located within walking distance of Parklane Elementary School, your daily commute becomes a breeze.The real gem of this property is the enormous fenced backyard, perfect for families and pets. Enjoy secure outdoor play, gardening, or simply relaxing on weekends. Host barbecues and create lasting memories in this generous space.Schedule a viewing today to experience the comfort and convenience of this 3-bedroom bungalow with refinished hardwood floors and a spacious fenced backyard, all within walking distance of Parklane Elementary School. Your new chapter begins here!
